docs.text: Welcome to WaterManagerDB docs This web app facilitates reporting of water management operations to other organizations. The initial goal is to help water conservation districts communicate with local and state governments. However, the interface may eventually be developed to be more general. For code visit github.org/NMWDI/WaterManagerDB . Links API Docs
